# AI / planning working artifacts — kept locally, never committed.
# These are the brainstorm specs, subagent execution plans, and
# session resume/QA scratch the team uses while building, not part of
# the product. Product + human docs (docs/TESTING.md,
# docs/how-do-i-get-my-data.md) stay tracked.
/SESSION_HANDOFF.md
/CREDS_NEEDED.md
/docs/E2E_STATUS.md
/docs/plans/
/docs/superpowers/
packages/*/docs/superpowers/

